# ONNX Runtime Web WASM assets. Copied from the installed onnxruntime-web
# package by `scripts/copy-ort-wasm.mjs` (run automatically by the app's
# build), not committed to git. Served same-origin under /models/ort/ so
# nothing is fetched from a CDN at runtime (CLAUDE.md; §1.3/§8).
*.wasm
*.mjs
!.gitignore
!README.md
